column10: I had a perfect stay at Oliver's apartment!  The building was situated behind other buildings and so the apartment was always quiet despite being located in such a bustling urban area.  The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!

The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit! The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!

column10: I had a perfect stay at Oliver's apartment!  The building was situated behind other buildings and so the apartment was always quiet despite being located in such a bustling urban area.  The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!

The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!

The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit! column10: I had a perfect stay at Oliver's apartment!  The building was situated behind other buildings and so the apartment was always quiet despite being located in such a bustling urban area.  The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!

column10: I had a perfect stay at Oliver's apartment!  The building was situated behind other buildings and so the apartment was always quiet despite being located in such a bustling urban area.  The location was fantastic and so convenient to groceries, restaurants, shopping and transit!  Oliver was warm and friendly and very helpful in providing suggestions for places to visit that were customized to my interests.  This apartment is a wonderful oasis in busy Berlin!
